{
  "stem": "894.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So to continue, I didn't want to speak to him, and he wanted to know why.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said, because you shoved this old man for no reason at all.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so he just shrugged it off, and he left.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was when we were lined up in the street, in the town, before we went to the train station.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then, when we got to the train, we were lucky if you can call it that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were lucky, because we got on first.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so my father took a corner in the wagon.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were sort of leaning against the wall.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because we found out later how lucky that was, because they packed the train so full.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't even know if some of the people were able to sit down all the time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they were just standing in the middle of the wagon.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we were able to sort of sit back and lean against the wall, so that was, you know, a really fortunate thing for us.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And my recollection then was, of course I was sitting next to my mother.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] It's like I can-- I can see it in my mind, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But I can't recall that many things happening.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I remember my father looking into a Hebrew book all three days that he was travelling.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I don't recall if he ever opened his mouth, even.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "My mother was sitting there saying that-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [CRYING] OK.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "She kept saying [SOBBING] that God should save the children.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[CRYING] She never even mentioned herself, I guess.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "She had some gut feeling that-- where we're going.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And maybe she heard enough, or maybe she could see the situation.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
